# Migration & Upgrade — <%= appName %>

Enterprise-safe upgrades for CLI, plugins, templates, and generated projects.

## Safety rules

1. **Never overwrite user changes** unless `--force` is set
2. **Backup** key files before project upgrades
3. Write **migration records** under `.mycli/migrations/`
4. Emit **UPGRADE_REPORT.md** after every run

## Scopes

| Scope | Purpose |
|-------|---------|
| `project` | Generated project scaffold migrations |
| `cli` | CLI compatibility notes |
| `plugin` | Installed plugin upgrade checks |
| `template` | Marketplace template upgrade stamps |

## Layout

```
src/migration/
  migrations/
  backup/
  reports/
.mycli/upgrade-backups/
.mycli/migrations/
UPGRADE_REPORT.md
MIGRATION.md
```

## CLI

```bash
my upgrade setup
my upgrade
my upgrade --scope project,template
my upgrade --dry-run
my upgrade --force
```

## Usage

```ts
import { registerMigration } from './src/migration/index.js';

const upgrade = registerMigration();
const plan = upgrade.plan('1.0.0', '1.1.0');
console.log(upgrade.render(plan));
```
